layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Service Areas — Philadelphia, Main Line, Delaware, Chester, Montgomery & Bucks Counties
description: Countertop fabrication and installation across Greater Philadelphia — the Main Line, Delaware County, Chester County, Montgomery County, Bucks County, and the city itself.
permalink: /service-areas/
faq:
  - q: Do you install countertops in Philadelphia?
    a: Yes. We fabricate granite, quartz, and marble countertops at our own shop in Lansdowne and install throughout Philadelphia — Chestnut Hill, Manayunk, Center City, and the surrounding neighborhoods.
  - q: Do you serve Delaware County?
    a: Yes — our fabrication shop is in Lansdowne, in the heart of Delaware County. We install in Media, Havertown, Springfield, Newtown Square, Drexel Hill, and across the county.
  - q: Do you serve Chester County?
    a: Yes. We regularly install countertops, tile, and cabinets in West Chester, Malvern, Paoli, and throughout Chester County.
  - q: Do you install in Bucks County?
    a: Yes. Bucks County projects — Doylestown, Newtown, Yardley, and nearby — are within our regular installation range.
  - q: Where can I see slabs in person?
    a: Our showroom at 130 E Lancaster Ave in Ardmore displays full-size quartz, granite, marble, and natural stone slabs, plus our Daltile tile selection and cabinet door lines. Open Monday through Saturday, Sunday by appointment.
  - q: Is there a charge for estimates?
    a: No — estimates are free. Tell us about your project and we call back within one business day, usually the same afternoon.
---

